{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_12_03",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――極烙拉麺の広告撮影　前日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7433.3333333,
          "startTime": 7.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は忙しかった……。腹が……減ったな……\n……本当に……腹が減った……",
      "startTime": 8.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3799.999999999999,
          "startTime": 12.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、力貸して下さい！\nこのままじゃうち、食欲に負けてしまいます",
      "startTime": 16.5663265546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……優？　どうしたんだ、こんな夜更けに\nご飯、お腹一杯食べたいよな。分かるよ、俺もだ",
      "startTime": 24.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "はい……この時間、寮でみんな晩ご飯食べてるから\n誘惑が多くて……それで事務所に避難して来たんです",
      "startTime": 35.0655552785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、{user}さん？\n手に持ってる、ええ匂いのそれ……なんです？",
      "startTime": 43.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺の手に、いい匂い……？　……うわっ！\nな、なんで俺はカップ麺を手に持ってるんだ？",
      "startTime": 52.2768108714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……。うち、{user}さんのこと\n同志やと思ってたのに……裏切ったんですか……？",
      "startTime": 60.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すまない……事務所に戻ってからの記憶がないんだ\n無意識にカップ麺を食べようとしていたんだな、俺",
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "謝らんとって下さい。うちと同じ\nダイエットメニューで過ごすの自体、無理やったんです",
      "startTime": 76.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、撮影直前までよく付き合ってくれました\nほら、どうぞ食べて下さい……うちの目の前で",
      "startTime": 84.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ここで！？　優の前でか？　……食べ辛いな……\n……あの、優も一口くらい、食べるか？",
      "startTime": 96.246143844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "お気持ちだけ受け取っておきます\nうち、明日の撮影にベストな状態で臨みたいですから",
      "startTime": 103.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そのためにも、今日の夕飯は我慢しないといけません\nうちはプロですから。一晩くらい大丈夫です",
      "startTime": 113.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、トレーナーさんは大丈夫って言ってましたけど\n最近、減量が少し停滞してて……カップ麺……カップ麺",
      "startTime": 122.7350094728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ダイエット中、しかも本番直前に誘惑して悪かった\n……だからその、俺のカップ麺を返してくれないか？",
      "startTime": 137.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "うちのメンタルはフランスパン並にカチカチですから\n目の前でカップ麺を食べてる人がいても、平気です",
      "startTime": 146.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……優の意志の固さはよく分かったよ\nだから、まずはカップ麺から手を離してくれないか？",
      "startTime": 155.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、何言ってるんです？\n……はっ！　うちいつの間にカップ麺を……！？",
      "startTime": 164.7147809304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、うちの気持ちとは裏腹に、手が……\n手がカップ麺に、吸い寄せられてまう……！",
      "startTime": 172.600012207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、一口だけでも食べた方が\nいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 178.8333455403,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6161.3027635000035,
          "startTime": 184.9946483038
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "ダメです、うちをこれ以上……これ以上\n誘惑せんとって下さいー！",
      "startTime": 183.7912075872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……ちゃんと寮に帰れたか、後で確認しておこう\nそれにしても、優の精神が心配だ。なんとかしないと",
      "startTime": 191.100012207,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7933.321126300001,
          "startTime": 199.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――極烙拉麺の広告撮影　当日",
      "startTime": 197.3810760578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.8810760578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "広告の撮影、お疲れ様。凄く良かったよ\nダイエットも激辛対策も、よく頑張ったな",
      "startTime": 204.3666737874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.0695148866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、衣装はピッタリでしたし撮影もバッチリでした\n激辛料理にも、随分と慣れました",
      "startTime": 213.1666737874,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.9928793000036,
          "startTime": 215.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 216.4804216465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "あ、スタッフさんが呼んでます。写真チェックですって\nうちと一緒に一番いい写真、選んで下さいね？",
      "startTime": 221.2333404541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "……自分で言うのもなんですけどええ写真が撮れました\nダイエットを頑張った甲斐があります",
      "startTime": 232.0666737874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "これで、極烙拉麺さんにもお客さんにも\n今のうちの、ベストを見せられると思います",
      "startTime": 238.5999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "……全部、{user}さんがうちを\n支えてくれたおかげです。本当にありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 244.0333292643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "……って、{user}さん！？\nなんでそんな感極まった顔してるんです？",
      "startTime": 251.4666585285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "優の頑張りを見てたからかな……\n込み上げるものがあってな……",
      "startTime": 258.6999979654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 262.1026463351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……優。この後、優の好きな極烙拉麺を\n食べに行かないか？",
      "startTime": 267.4717722645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "え？　で、でもうちはダイエット中ですから\nイベント当日まで、そんなええ物、食べる資格は……",
      "startTime": 273.4666625975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 278.0560561419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
